INSERT INTO `OpenMics` (`OpenMicID`,`Type`,`Title`,`Description`,`DateTime`,`Signup`,`CreatorUserID`,`Duration`,`DurationUnit`,`EndDateTime`,`Frequency`,`CreatedAt`,`UpdatedAt`,`VenueID`,`PhotoURL`) VALUES (10,'Music','Open Mike at The Carbon Arc','How serious am I about Open Mikes? It\'s the day before the last day of the first month of the year and I\'m already packing up for tomorrow night. It\'ll be cold but it will rock! This Thursday we are going to fill the Carbon Arc with artists of all walks of life and ages. There will be covers and originals, good food & drink, family & friends. So come out, see a movie and stop by the Open Mike and see some real aspiring artists. Plus it\'s the end of Martin Luther King month and the beginning of Black history month all in one go. Come out, be topical or be anti-topical but lets play some music eh?!','2019-02-01 21:30:00.000000','2019-02-01 21:00:00.000000',1,2,'Hours','2019-02-01 23:30:00.000000','Weekly','2019-01-31 19:04:25.125255','2019-01-31 19:04:25.125257',10,'https://i.imgur.com/rMfw0wb.jpg');
