INSERT INTO `OpenMics` (`OpenMicID`,`Type`,`Title`,`Description`,`DateTime`,`Signup`,`CreatorUserID`,`Duration`,`DurationUnit`,`EndDateTime`,`Frequency`,`CreatedAt`,`UpdatedAt`,`VenueID`,`PhotoURL`) VALUES (21,'Music','Open Mic Night','Every Thursday at 9pm, head to Logan Bar for the best Open Mic Night in Chicago! Our host each week is the talented John Kimler, and we have a variety of professional equipment available for use.  The fun starts at 9pm and our sponsor is Two Brothers Brewing, which means we will always have a featured $5 draft!\r\n\r\nGrab some friends and come share some of that hidden talent on the Logan Stage!','2019-02-07 21:00:00.000000','2019-02-07 20:00:00.000000',1,4,'Hours','2019-02-08 01:00:00.000000','Weekly','2019-01-31 23:54:07.806544','2019-01-31 23:54:07.806547',21,'https://i.imgur.com/BDtCoyj.jpg');
INSERT INTO `OpenMics` (`OpenMicID`,`Type`,`Title`,`Description`,`DateTime`,`Signup`,`CreatorUserID`,`Duration`,`DurationUnit`,`EndDateTime`,`Frequency`,`CreatedAt`,`UpdatedAt`,`VenueID`,`PhotoURL`) VALUES (22,'Music','Open Mic Night (Sponsored by Shure)','OUR WEEKLY OPEN MIC NIGHTS ARE HELD ON MONDAYS AT UNCOMMON GROUND LAKEVIEW AND TUESDAYS AT UNCOMMON GROUND EDGEWATER. WE OPEN UP OUR STAGE TO ARTISTS AND MUSICIANS OF ALL AGES AND BACKGROUNDS. ALL OF OUR OPEN MIC EVENTS ARE HOSTED  BY ERIC QUIGLEY.\r\nSIGN-UP BEGINS AT 7PM. THE OPEN MIC STARTS AT 8PM AND RUNS UNTIL 10PM, OR WHENEVER THE LIST IS COMPLETED. IT IS HIGHLY RECOMMENDED ALL ARTISTS ARRIVE CLOSE TO 7PM TO GUARANTEE A SPOT.  THE LENGTH OF STAGE TIME FOR EACH ARTIST RANGES FROM 5 MINUTES (1 SONG) TO 15 MINUTES (2-3 SONGS), DEPENDING ON THE NUMBER OF PERFORMERS THAT NIGHT.','2019-02-05 20:00:00.000000','2019-02-05 19:00:00.000000',1,2,'Hours','2019-02-05 22:00:00.000000','Weekly','2019-01-31 23:59:41.088742','2019-01-31 23:59:41.088745',22,'https://i.imgur.com/PDUQAPz.png');
